feat: add multilingual support (i18n)

New Features:
- Complete i18n system with support for Chinese, English, Japanese, Korean
- Automatic language detection based on title text analysis
- Manual language override via --lang parameter
- Multilingual prompts for extraction and semantic analysis
- Language-aware error messages

Changes:
- lib/i18n.js (new) - Internationalization module with prompt templates
- lib/extractor.js - Updated to use i18n prompts
- lib/smart-detector.js - Updated semantic analysis for multilingual
- index.js - Added --lang parameter to knowledge_summarize tool
- .env.example - Added DEFAULT_LANGUAGE configuration
- MULTILINGUAL.md (new) - Comprehensive multilingual usage guide

Usage:
- Auto-detect: /knowledge_summarize --title "Your Title" --category "Category"
- Manual: /knowledge_summarize --title "标题" --category "架构" --lang en
- Config: Set DEFAULT_LANGUAGE=en in .env
